                    <msContents>
                        <summary>
                            List of <foreign>biruda</foreign>s engraved on the fourt and lower tiers of the bases of the chapels of the <foreign>prākāra</foreign> of the Rājasiṃheśvara. This list no. 4 is shorter than than the lists nos. 1-3 since its ornate Siddhamātr̥kā requires more space taht the the scripts of the other lists. Only the chapels nos. <seg rend="check">1-20</seg> are inscribed on this tier. For the first, second and third tiers, see inscription <ref target="DHARMA_INSPallava00055.xml">Pallava 55</ref>. See also inscription <ref target="DHARMA_INSPallava00385.xml">Pallava 385</ref> on the base of the <foreign>prākāra</foreign> of the Mahendreśvara.
                            
                        </summary>
                    </msContents>
                    <physDesc>
                        <handDesc>
                            <p/>
                        </handDesc>
                    </physDesc>
                </msDesc>
            </sourceDesc>
        </fileDesc>
        <revisionDesc>
            <change who="part:emfr" when="2026-06-07" status="draft">creation of the file</change>
        </revisionDesc>
